# ============================================
# PUBLIC REPO: overview docs + project metadata
# ============================================
# Published to GitHub: README, structure, LICENSE, CONTRIBUTING,
# CODE_OF_CONDUCT, mise.toml, and icon. Source → private repo.

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Project metadata & policy files
!.gitignore
!/LICENSE
!/CONTRIBUTING.md
!/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
!/mise.toml
!/README.md

# Project structure doc
!/docs/
/docs/*
!/docs/PROJECT-STRUCTURE.md

# README icon
!/resources/
/resources/*
!/resources/icon.svg

# ============================================
# Never publish
# ============================================
Internal/
internal/
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
